# Controls and Compliance Checklist of a fictitious company
# named Botium Toys - a toy manufacturer and distributor based in the US.

# In a scale of 1 to 10, the risk factor of the security posture 
# of Botium Toys is 8. Which is an indication of how vulnerable the
# company and its assets are to any cyber attack from threat actors.


